data.description: The potential is endless with this 3 bedroom 2 full bath ranch home sitting on 2.23 acres and having a full walkout basement just waiting for someone to finish it into family space.   The living room, dining room and kitchen are open and have access to the deck to the back.  This home has the right stuff with walk in closets, a pantry, split floorplan, the kitchen appliances to include a refrigerator, range and dishwasher, and a covered front porch.  The 2 car attached garage has extra space for some storage.  The location is great, back from the road with a huge backyard should you want to put in a barn or storage shed.  The home needs TLC, new flooring or carpet throughout and repair work on the a/c.This property is a find if you want to make it your own and bring it back to its best condition.
